These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, pumpkin, cucumber, kale
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, april, february, may
1. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
3. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating kale is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
5. the person who's birthday is in october is the person eating pumpkin##1
6. the person eating cucumber is the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Food      | kale  | peach | pumpkin  | cucumber |
| Birthday   | february | may      | october | april |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, blues, indie, reggae
House: colonial, victorian, cape-cod, palace
1. the fan of blues is between the colonial house and the palace house##2
2. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
3. the colonial house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
4. the colonial house is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
5. the victorian house is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | indie | blues   | d&b |
| House           | cape-cod      | colonial    | victorian | palace      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, horse, snake, bird
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, turquise, coral, purple
1. the owner of the horse is the person who likes turquise##1
2. the person who likes purple is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the left of the person who likes mauve##5
4. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
5. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the person who likes purple##5
6. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the person who likes coral##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Pet        | horse | frog | snake     | bird |
| Color   | turquise  | purple   | coral | mauve    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta, almond-milk, milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, surfing, climbing, golf
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
3. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is surfing##2
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
5. the person who's sport is golf is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage         | almond-milk | iced-tea | fanta | milk |
| Sport   | golf   | climbing     | surfing    | cricket       |

