.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
House: tower, cottage, townhouse, wooden
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, pall-mall, fonseca, old-henry
1. the wooden house is somewhere to the left of the blend-smoker##5
2. the wooden house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
3. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
5. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
6. the wooden house is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| House          | townhouse | wooden   | tower   | cottage    |
| Cigar   | pall-mall  | old-henry | blend | fonseca |

