.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, house, reggae, rock
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, cooking, chess, woodworking
1. the fan of rock is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of soul is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the fan of rock and the person who's hobby is chess##2
4. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Music-Genre           | soul | house | rock | reggae |
| Hobby   | chess        | woodworking     | drawing       | cooking   |

