.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
4 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, poker, domino
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, british, nigerian, french
1. the british is the person playing domino##1
2. the person playing bridge is between the person playing mah-jongg and the nigerian##2
3. the russian is in an even position##4
4. the french is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
5. the person playing bridge is in an even position##4
6. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the british##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | bridge  | poker  | domino   |
| Nationality           | french  | russian | nigerian | british |

