.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, fanta, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, rugby, ice-hockey, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | lemonade     | iced-tea | fanta     | juice   |
| Sport    | water-polo | rugby  | ice-hockey | sailing |

