.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, polish, russian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, superhero, disaster, action
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the brazilian##1
2. the polish is on the left of the russian##1
3. the brazilian is on the left of the polish##1
4. the canadian is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
5. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
6. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | brazilian | polish | russian   | canadian |
| Movie-Genre       | family       | disaster   | action | superhero |

