There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, mauve, orange, aquamarine
1. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
2. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the left of the farmhouse house##5
3. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the right of the futuristic house##5
4. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the right of the person who likes aquamarine##5
5. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the left of the modern house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| House   | futuristic | ranch-style       | modern   | farmhouse        |
| Color      | mauve  | aquamarine | lavender | orange |

