.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, onion, pomegranate, eggplant
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, blend, siglo, havana
1. the person eating kiwi is somewhere to the left of the person eating onion##5
2. the siglo-smoker is the person eating pomegranate##1
3. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person eating onion##1
4. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the right of the siglo-smoker##5
5. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the left of the old-henry-smoker##5
6. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
7. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the right of the old-henry-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Food   | kiwi | onion   | pomegranate | eggplant     |
| Cigar   | blend     | old-henry | siglo  | havana |

