.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, chestnut, light-blue, blood-red
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, french, chinese
1. the chinese is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the chinese is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the left of the dutch##5
4. the person who likes aquamarine is the french##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the right of the person who likes light-blue##5
6. the dutch is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Color   | aquamarine | light-blue        | blood-red        | chestnut |
| Nationality         | french  | chinese | argentine | dutch |

