.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-13::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, august, october, may
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, biathlon, cricket, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Birthday         | october | may | august | november |
| Sport   | snowboarding     | water-polo  | biathlon  | cricket    |

