1. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person eating corn##5
2. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person eating broccoli##5
3. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
4. the person eating asparagus is the pall-mall-smoker##1
5. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the right of the montecristo-smoker##5
6. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Cigar   | aristoff  | montecristo | cain | pall-mall |
| Food   | corn | broccoli | nectarine   | asparagus  |

