.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, orange, broccoli, cauliflower
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, tram, van, scooter
1. the person eating cauliflower is between the person eating broccoli and the person eating orange##2
2. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
4. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
5. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Food   | cherry | broccoli  | cauliflower      | orange |
| Transport     | van    | scooter | tram | roller   |

