.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, balloon-flower, iris, azalea
City: miami, rome, new-york, marseilles
1. the person who growsiris is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsazalea is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person traveling to miami is in an even position##4
5. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the left of the person who growsazalea##5
6. the person who growsiris is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person traveling to rome##2
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Flower      | amaryllis   | iris  | balloon-flower      | azalea       |
| City   | new-york | marseilles | rome | miami |

