2. the person who growsdaffodil is the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Flower   | balloon-flower     | lily | bellflower | daffodil |
| Beverage     | tea | hot-chocolate    | water    | lemonade |

