4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, old-henry, alhambra, chaman
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere to the right of the chaman-smoker##5
3. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
4. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5
5. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is rowing and the old-henry-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Sport      | lacrosse     | rowing | water-polo     | cycling |
| Cigar   | alhambra | chaman  | baccarat | old-henry        |

