.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, january, april, november
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, tennis, skiing, volleyball
1. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's birthday is in january##2
2. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5
3. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Birthday         | april   | november   | march       | january   |
| Sport   | skiing | tennis | cricket | volleyball |

