.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, sudoku, collecting, rock-climbing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, may, april, june
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's birthday is in december##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby        | sudoku     | rock-climbing | woodworking | collecting |
| Birthday   | april | june | may      | december        |

 